                            Are you sure you want to delete <span id="deleteContactName" class="font-medium text-slate-900"></span>? This action cannot be undone and will permanently remove all contact information.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-end space-x-3">
